{"tid":351124,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"毛囊角化中醫/西醫推介","createTime":"2017-08-07T17:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T05:50:07.000Z","uid":14024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9c70110a7ca074f45e3699cd6d75a89821f64942","tid":351124,"uid":14024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:51:06.000Z","msg":"小弟有左毛囊角化都有左一段日子<br />\n之前睇過林渭新醫生<br />\n佢就開潤膚膏比我<br />\n想試下有無巴絲睇過醫生有無其他方法可以減輕情況<br />\n所以係到睇下大家有無介紹<br />\n中醫如果有效都求推介<br />\n<br />\n同埋睇下有無巴絲都有呢個病，可以分享下有無方法改善問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fcdc4fffc97a102cd0cc1719e3c15b41d399e79","tid":351124,"uid":24423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56577c3fea4e3f929d36e43e7e5e6f0337a104d8","tid":351124,"uid":25170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T18:24:48.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"43c1828a8f12b730bbe45aa1bca6795f9058bf10","tid":351124,"uid":14024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fb36a24ac4fde16d7072887ce11c46490e5891","tid":351124,"uid":81241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:22:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0df6ae43fbd7cad7e7f55ec87214fef7212317ad","tid":351124,"uid":14024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:08:27.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkg